{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "This precisely crafted workflow optimizes accuracy and fosters robustness and efficiency in our methodology.",
    "ModelFITMI's approach innovatively integrates LDMs with the latest image and text integration advancements, drawing inspiration from successful precedents and extending their capabilities.",
    "The backbone of our method lies in adopting LDMs, which have been shown to surpass the capabilities of traditional GANs in image generation tasks.",
    "This shift was initially inspired by the work presented by Rombach et al. [27], which mitigated some of the inherent limitations of GANs.",
    "The LaDI-VTON model [22] adapted LDMs by effectively using latent space for more detailed and controllable image synthesis.The standard input structure of these models has been modified to accommodate the complexities of virtual try-on better."
  ],
